/index.php?title=In_the_Night_Kitchen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Gottlieb, Richard M. (2008). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=LLcBV9ghpuAC&amp;pg=PA186&amp;lpg=PA186\">\"Maurice Sendak's Trilogy: Disappointment, Fury, and Their Transformation through Art\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Psychoanalytic_Study_of_the_Child\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Psychoanalytic Study of the Child\">Psychoanalytic Study of the Child</a></i>. <b>63</b>: 186\u2013217. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-300-14099-6\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-300-14099-6\">978-0-300-14099-6</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19449794\">19449794</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Psychoanalytic+Study+of+the+Child&amp;rft.atitle=Maurice+Sendak%27s+Trilogy%3A+Disappointment%2C+Fury%2C+and+Their+Transformation+through+Art&amp;rft.volume=63&amp;rft.pages=186-217&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F19449794&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-300-14099-6&amp;rft.aulast=Gottlieb&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+M.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DLLcBV9ghpuAC%26pg%3DPA186%26lpg%3DPA186&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIn+the+Night+Kitchen\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\"